{"tid":1108967,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"央視網批B站低俗內容氾濫遭多名市民投訴","createTime":"2019-04-16T07:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T09:21:49.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4a09451d0a13916a3d24e92f47e041991daa8df1","tid":1108967,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"據央視網微信公眾號消息，央視網今日發文《13歲讓女老師懷孕，15歲的同居生活&hellip;知名網站被曝低俗內容氾濫》，文中提到多名市民投訴B站包含大量大尺度動漫和低俗內容，部分內容涉及到師生戀、亂倫戀等，引發家長擔憂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCZppCn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCZppCn.jpg&h=be8de2f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文章中表示，有記者4月8日登陸B站，點擊主站番劇連載動畫一欄，就看到名為《15歲今天開始同居生活》的動漫作品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZK2yhXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZK2yhXt.jpg&h=a41b77bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而影視雜談欄目下，一則《日本小伙愛上自己的女老師醉酒後終於得償所願》的視頻已有435.3萬的點擊量，1274人同步彈幕討論該劇。而在相關劇集裡，涉及到亂倫、國外限制級等內容也都有幾十萬甚至上百萬的播放量。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wpqv4CA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpqv4CA.jpg&h=67c423d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，文中還稱B站的部分視頻標題十分低俗，如《13歲男孩讓女老師懷孕這部爆笑喜劇我看沒那麼簡單》《女生看你上廁所是什麼經歷》等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zix2VKw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZix2VKw.jpg&h=35fc83e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日，IT之家前往B站官方查詢，發現《15歲，今天開始同居生活》、《日本小伙愛上自己的老師》等已經搜不到相關視頻。目前B站官方尚未對此給出相應回复。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQOxywc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQOxywc.jpg&h=2c0200d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b1SqTwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb1SqTwm.jpg&h=f978f37d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n央視網最後呼籲，不要讓互聯網中的軟色情侵蝕了懵懂無知的孩子們，很顯然這種傷害一旦造成就是終身的，因為孩子們會由淺入深從而走上歧途。"},{"pid":"c747008905e911b16ffc42dbc6f21165c77faab5","tid":1108967,"uid":49391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:19:31.000Z","msg":"呢D片YOUTUBE仲搵到,只係一D電影速食片<br />\n好懷疑央視根本無睇過D片,單憑標題就搞批鬥"},{"pid":"7f7a9d798eb852de1cf44437686349c782aea733","tid":1108967,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"045fb0d8925e4aac4e0b634f2692503246eec295","tid":1108967,"uid":130563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:24:53.000Z","msg":"其實係咪背後俾唔夠錢政府"},{"pid":"d848d6f935c74ccd97992ba394407f403aafde8c","tid":1108967,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3bab3ce2eba89f2519f6e25394b175c199e8381","tid":1108967,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"都係E站好"},{"pid":"cef69d5f8d77aa776707f58738c403bfc2388303","tid":1108967,"uid":105678,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"不嬲全世界出事都會搞acg轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n大陸之前搞王者榮耀係因為蒙古大選，今次會係咩原因？"},{"pid":"3f9ad499e328ba920a6c564a8e72ff5032553b2d","tid":1108967,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cef69d5f8d77aa776707f58738c403bfc2388303","tid":1108967,"uid":105678,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"不嬲全世界出事都會搞acg轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n大陸之前搞王者榮耀係因為蒙古大選，今次會係咩原因？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"正評左"},{"pid":"e33e16c051eb63a5cbb8afac2ca1233545a688ec","tid":1108967,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcc0fefbb1ad0629bfab045ec00dddabb7a16db3","tid":1108967,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e33e16c051eb63a5cbb8afac2ca1233545a688ec","tid":1108967,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d848d6f935c74ccd97992ba394407f403aafde8c","tid":1108967,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7a9d798eb852de1cf44437686349c782aea733","tid"